description: Token to be used to make token lists.

isDismissible.description:
Determines if token has dismissible feature or not. If true, `onDismiss`
is required.

isDraggable.description: Shows an icon indicating that the token is draggable

onDismiss.description:
Function to call that dismisses the token. Required if the token is
dismissible.

order.description: Show a number indicating the token's order

style.description: Determines style of token depending on priority level
